PHONE_REDACTEDT05:PORT:PORT.603706Z	    9 Query	insert into daily_analysis_reports (analysis_confidence,analysis_scope_note,day,executive_summary,generated_at,misconfiguration_signals,system_behavior_analysis,user_behavior_analysis) values ('Analysis confidence is high due to the large volume of data available for review.','The analysis scope is limited to a single calendar day, specifically March 23rd, 2026 (IST).','PHONE_REDACTED','On the 23rd of March, 2026 (IST), a total of 190 lead submissions were made with a success ratio of 74.74%. Notable findings include high user activity from EMAIL_REDACTED and EMAIL_REDACTED, duplicates being the primary cause of failure, and all rate limit failures not associated with any specific final page.','PHONE_REDACTED:PORT:PORT.594277','A high number of duplicate leads suggests potential misconfiguration or integration issues with the lead submission system.','The system handled a daily peak of 19 attempts per minute and recorded no burst minutes during the analyzed timeframe.','The users EMAIL_REDACTED and EMAIL_REDACTED exhibited significantly high activity levels with a combined total of 290 attempts resulting in 169 successful submissions, representing 58.62% of the day''s total volume.')
